# Case Study: BakedBudz Store v1 → v2  
**Role:** Systems Architect & Technical Operations Lead  
**Platforms:** Blaze POS API, WooCommerce, Custom PHP Plugin, WordPress, Webhooks, Tookan/Onfleet-style dispatch systems, SMS/Loyalty platforms, ID Verification APIs

---

## Overview

This case study documents the full lifecycle of designing, architecting, and co-developing both versions of the BakedBudz eCommerce platform — from the original Blaze-powered v1 store to the fully independent v2 rebuild.

Across both versions, I was responsible for:
- defining the system architecture  
- mapping API behavior and webhook flows  
- validating developer work  
- reverse-engineering undocumented behavior  
- ensuring operational integrity across ordering, catalog, inventory, dispatch, payments, and loyalty  

The result was a fully functioning multi-system eCommerce & delivery platform capable of supporting 50+ orders/day with automated verification, dispatch routing, catalog sync, and loyalty logic.

